      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) must confirm expected spatial and temporal convergence rates for all relevant solver components.",
      "rationale": "Convergence studies demonstrate first-order spatial accuracy in near-wall regions; MMS testing was not performed for the hemolysis transport equation. Achieved level 2 due to incomplete verification scope."
