      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs (blood viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) must be characterized with probability distributions and propagated through Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on flow boundary conditions but hemolysis model coefficients (C, alpha, beta in power-law) were treated as deterministic. Input uncertainty for the constitutive model is uncharacterized."
