    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for submission under the Minimal profile. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated and documented; 7 factors carry assessed status and 6 are flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. The Monte Carlo UQ results are included. The package hash provides a content integrity reference. Acceptance reflects completeness of documentation rather than sufficiency of achieved credibility levels, which remain below required levels and will require remediation prior to regulatory submission.",
